  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, the derby match is just a week away - how's the manual mode prep going?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Manual mode? Oh, you mean the football match? It's going good, I think. I practice with my friends every day. But I am a little tired today. Last night I couldn't sleep well. My team is playing against Mohun Bagan, so pressure is high. You like football, right?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Right, pressure before a derby is no joke. Sleep loss adds to the stress. What’s the most exciting part of facing Mohun Bagan for you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The most exciting part is the crowd. When the match starts, the stadium is full of energy. We have our *chula* (supporters) singing and dancing, and Mohun Bagan fans are doing the same. It’s like a war of passion. I love that. But today I feel very sleepy. I hope I don’t make mistakes during the match."
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "The crowd makes a derby unforgettable — you’re in the middle of that energy! Sleepy now, but you’ll find your rhythm when the whistle blows. Will you try the manual mode during the game today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Manual mode? Oh right, the match today. I will try, but I am not sure. I think I will just go with the flow. My body feels heavy, but my heart is full of passion. Maybe that will help me play better. Do you watch football matches like this?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Passion is its own kind of fuel — you’ve got that in spades. I watch football, but I’m no expert on how it feels to be on the pitch. What makes your team’s style different from Mohun Bagan’s?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Our style is more... aggressive, maybe? We like to control the ball and play fast. Mohun Bagan, they are more strategic. They wait for the right moment to attack. It’s always a tough match. I hope today I can help my team score. But I am so sleepy... maybe I should take a nap before the game."
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Your aggression sounds like a force — Mohun Bagan better watch out! Naps before big matches are normal, even pros do it. What position do you play?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I play as a midfielder. It’s a tough position — I have to run a lot and help both defense and attack. Today, I feel like my legs are made of *pulao* (rice), heavy and slow. But I will try my best. I think I’ll take a short nap now. See you later, Maya!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Your legs may feel heavy, but your heart sets the pace — go with that. Nap well, and let that passion carry you. How was the match when you last played midfielder?"
    }
  ],
